### Phase 4 — Ticket comments and unified timeline.
###
### Builds on Phase 3. Promote agent/admin roles via SQL once after registration.

@host = http://localhost:8080
@customerEmail = customer@example.com
@agentEmail    = agent@example.com
@adminEmail    = admin@example.com
@password      = password123

@customerToken = paste-customer-token
@agentToken    = paste-agent-token
@adminToken    = paste-admin-token
@ticketId      = paste-ticket-uuid
@commentId     = paste-comment-uuid

### 1. Customer adds a comment
POST {{host}}/api/v1/tickets/{{ticketId}}/comments
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "body": "The problem still happens after restarting the device."
}

### 2. Agent adds a comment (must be assigned)
POST {{host}}/api/v1/tickets/{{ticketId}}/comments
Authorization: Bearer {{agentToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "body": "Investigating the auth service logs."
}

### 3. List comments (chronological)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/tickets/{{ticketId}}/comments
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}

### 4. Edit own comment (paste @commentId from step 1)
PUT {{host}}/api/v1/tickets/{{ticketId}}/comments/{{commentId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "body": "Updated: the problem only happens on the Android app build 1.2.3."
}

### 5. Non-author cannot edit (EXPECTED 403)
PUT {{host}}/api/v1/tickets/{{ticketId}}/comments/{{commentId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{agentToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "body": "trying to edit someone else's"
}

### 6. Admin can edit any comment
PUT {{host}}/api/v1/tickets/{{ticketId}}/comments/{{commentId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "body": "[moderated by admin]"
}

### 7. Delete a comment
DELETE {{host}}/api/v1/tickets/{{ticketId}}/comments/{{commentId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}

### 8. Unified timeline — histories + comments, sorted ascending
GET {{host}}/api/v1/tickets/{{ticketId}}/timeline
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}
